summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Photo Renamer system. Backend APIs working perfectly with 911 Excel mappings loaded. Frontend loads correctly with light theme and responsive design. File upload UI present but programmatic testing limited by browser security.

integration_issues.issue: Cannot programmatically test file upload due to browser security restrictions
integration_issues.note: Manual testing required for complete file upload workflow

passed_tests: Backend API GET /api/ - responds correctly with 'Photo Renamer API'
Backend API GET /api/excel-mapping - returns 911 mappings from remote Excel file
Backend API POST /api/process-images - processes and renames images correctly
Backend API GET /api/download-zip/{session_id} - downloads ZIP successfully
Frontend loads correctly with light theme and proper branding
Frontend displays 911 mappings in scrollable table
Frontend search functionality filters mappings correctly
Frontend refresh button works and reloads mappings
Frontend upload dropzone is present and accessible
Frontend process button correctly disabled when no files uploaded
Frontend responsive design adapts to different screen sizes

success_percentage.frontend: 95% - All UI elements working, file upload needs manual testing
